==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Ribbed
<hw>Ribbed</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Furnished
or formed with ribs; <as>as, a <ex>ribbed</ex> cylinder; <ex>ribbed</ex>
cloth</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Mining)</fld> <def>Intercalated with slate; -- said
of a seam of coal.</def> <rj><au>Raymond.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Ribbing</ent>⟦br⟧
